// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1318 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 0407a7ab-20db-5251-8874-840bd7f3f1c6

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.10*")
